A vintage-style architectural blueprint illustration showing an Olympic swimming pool viewed from above, with distinct parallel lanes filled with flowing water rendered in deep blues and teals. Each lane contains different abstract geometric symbols representing interconnected systems - gears, circuit patterns, organic flowing shapes, and structural frameworks - all moving in synchronized harmony toward a shared finish line. The water creates subtle connections between lanes through rippling waves. Aged paper texture with sepia-toned edges, technical drawing aesthetic with precise grid lines and measurement marks along the borders. Warm amber lighting creates depth and nostalgia. No people, no text.
